    <p>We're here to help! If you have any questions, issues, or feedback about StepChick, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@hadalcore.com">info@hadalcore.com</a></p>
    <p>We aim to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours.</p>

    <h2>Common Questions</h2>

    <h2>How do I restore my subscription?</h2>
    <p>Open the app, go to Settings, and tap "Restore Purchases." Your subscription will be restored automatically if you have an active subscription linked to your Apple ID.</p>

    <h2>How does StepChick track my steps?</h2>
    <p>StepChick reads step data from Apple Health. Make sure you've granted HealthKit permissions in the app. No data ever leaves your device without your consent.</p>

    <h2>How do I cancel my subscription?</h2>
    <p>Subscriptions are managed through your Apple ID. Go to Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions on your iPhone to manage or cancel your StepChick subscription.</p>

    <h2>I found a bug</h2>
    <p>Please email us at <a href="mailto:info@hadalcore.com">info@hadalcore.com</a> with a description of the issue and your device model. Screenshots are always helpful!</p>
